    wisdom:mechanism "Multiple systems contribute truth signals to collective understanding" ;
    wisdom:emergentIntelligence "Wisdom arises from truth propagation networks" ;
    wisdom:networkWisdom "Intelligence is property of the network, not individual nodes" .

