    wisdom:memoryWisdom "Append-only storage creates time-irreversible truth accumulation" ;
    wisdom:pulseWisdom "Rhythmic processing creates coherent information flow" ;
    wisdom:signalWisdom "Pure signal passing maintains truth integrity across boundaries" ;
    wisdom:supervisionWisdom "Resilient architecture enables continuous wisdom emergence" .

# Forbidden Wisdom Cuts - What Must Not Be Severed
